{"data":[{"id":561808071,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b144c9f2feadfa399a2603f7b1b4912e","url_token":"ding-chun-88","name":"定春","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/24c264d44_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/24c264d44_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b144c9f2feadfa399a2603f7b1b4912e","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":81,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561808071","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546003099,"updated_time":1546139690,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"comment_count":6,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我是个文科生，数学最多只学到微积分入门，不过我觉得这个问题用我们专业的话来说大概就是：如果高中生能获得诺贝尔文学奖，会被北大中文系保送吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e————————————————————————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2018.12.30改：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果高中生能破译所有甲骨文，会被北大中文系保送吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e被大家提醒了，诺奖并不是一个具体的科研成果，况且还是文学奖（丘吉尔还拿过文学奖），放在这里与哥德巴赫猜想比较不合适。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说到甲骨文，前几年媒体吹捧的“高考甲骨文考生”后续在这里：\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baijiahao.baidu.com/s%3Fid%3D1574423329106964%26wfr%3Dspider%26for%3Dpc\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e当年被破格录取的“甲骨文”作文考生, 你知道如今怎么样了吗?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e导师何崝：心静浮躁 吹起牛来比谁都厉害\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e这个两年中，感觉到他学校不是很踏实的。他就不是这块料，不是做学问的，非常浮躁。他吹起牛来比谁都厉害，很多书他都说读过了。像这样的一个学风，我们怎么能容忍呢?他在这个甲骨文方面还不是非常的突出。他只是认识一些甲骨文，好像是几百个吧。我们找一个中学生，培养他一两个月，他基本上就可以认识上千个甲骨文了。这个并不是什么大不了的事情。\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e如今泯然众人矣的黄蛉说：当初在高考的时候用甲骨文来写作文其实也只是逞一时之快，因为知道自己的成绩或许连本科都上不了，索性就破罐子破摔，让阅卷老师看看自己平时所学的不一样的东西，结果没想到反而因祸得福！\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e媒体舆论把“怪才”黄蛉推上了高峰，阴差阳错的社会又给了他让人羡慕的“特殊待遇”，可悲可叹，才学和性情却不与时俱进，最终还是被社会否定！简直是现代版《伤仲永》！\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我是个文科生，数学最多只学到微积分入门，不过我觉得这个问题用我们专业的话来说大概就是：如果高中生能获得诺贝尔文学奖，会被北大中文系保送吗？————————————————————————————————2018.12.30改：如果高中生能破译所有甲…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1149\u0026platform=deskt